  "content": "<div>\n<p>\nactualidad\n</p>\n<h2>■La clásica y anual feria de vinos comenzó el 22 de mayo y finaliza el lunes 10 de junio en los hipermercados Géant Parque Roosevelt y Nuevocentro. </h2>\n</div><div>\n<div><figure>\n<picture>\n<img alt=\"Hace 22 ediciones que el Salón del Vino de Géant es uno de los principales puntos de encuentro.\" srcset=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/f845188/2147483647/strip/true/crop/992x682+16+0/resize/1440x990!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2Fbc%2F5d%2F1de38a074622be98491751ffd755%2Fph-alvaro-portillo-1.jpg 1x, https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/9d21dc0/2147483647/strip/true/crop/992x682+16+0/resize/2880x1980!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2Fbc%2F5d%2F1de38a074622be98491751ffd755%2Fph-alvaro-portillo-1.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/f845188/2147483647/strip/true/crop/992x682+16+0/resize/1440x990!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2Fbc%2F5d%2F1de38a074622be98491751ffd755%2Fph-alvaro-portillo-1.jpg\" />\n</picture>\n<p>\n</p><figcaption>Hace 22 ediciones que el Salón del Vino de Géant es uno de los principales puntos de encuentro.</figcaption><p></p>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>Hace más de 20 ediciones que el Salón del Vino de Géant es uno de los principales puntos de encuentro y compra de vinos finos en nuestro país.</p><div>\n<figure>\n<picture>\n<img alt=\"Los miembros del Directorio Guillermo Vivo, Alicia Lalanne y.Rosina Pombo junto al CEO de GDU Jean Christophe Tijeras.\" srcset=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/36a6c7b/2147483647/strip/true/crop/998x768+0+0/resize/998x768!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F15%2Fdf%2Ffe5247c3431ebead92c58f31a9bb%2F1.jpg 1x, https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/dec9eee/2147483647/strip/true/crop/998x768+0+0/resize/1996x1536!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F15%2Fdf%2Ffe5247c3431ebead92c58f31a9bb%2F1.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/36a6c7b/2147483647/strip/true/crop/998x768+0+0/resize/998x768!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F15%2Fdf%2Ffe5247c3431ebead92c58f31a9bb%2F1.jpg\" />\n</picture>\n<p>\n</p><figcaption>Los miembros del Directorio Guillermo Vivo, Alicia Lalanne y.Rosina Pombo junto al CEO de GDU Jean Christophe Tijeras.</figcaption><p></p>\n</figure>\n</div><p>El evento, que se extiende a lo largo de 20 días, aglutina en esta oportunidad, a más de 56 stands con ofertas para todos los paladares. Son más de 50 opciones en los que se puede degustar, seleccionar y comprar etiquetas nacionales e importadas.</p><div>\n<figure>\n<picture>\n<img alt=\"Óscar Rodons Gerente de Compras Frescos en GDU, Martín Gómez, gerente de Marketing de GDU y Gustavo \nDenardi, gerente de Operaciones Géant.\" srcset=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/6b69997/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x718+0+0/resize/1024x718!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F56%2F49%2F059c2c5d4009aa727b7e1c4267f2%2F2.jpg 1x, https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/d8bd545/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x718+0+0/resize/2048x1436!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F56%2F49%2F059c2c5d4009aa727b7e1c4267f2%2F2.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/6b69997/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x718+0+0/resize/1024x718!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F56%2F49%2F059c2c5d4009aa727b7e1c4267f2%2F2.jpg\" />\n</picture>\n<p>\n</p><figcaption>Óscar Rodons Gerente de Compras Frescos en GDU, Martín Gómez, gerente de Marketing de GDU y Gustavo Denardi, gerente de Operaciones Géant.</figcaption><p></p>\n</figure>\n</div><p>Se trata de un multi espacio imprescindible para el intercambio entre enófilos y productores.</p><div>\n<figure>\n<picture>\n<img alt=\"María Eugenia Hernández, Adriana Anza y Guadalupe Irigoyen.\" srcset=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/84422ff/2147483647/strip/true/crop/502x768+0+0/resize/502x768!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F39%2F50%2F21af670d442692bb03db731afd9b%2F4.jpg 1x, https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/aa31774/2147483647/strip/true/crop/502x768+0+0/resize/1004x1536!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F39%2F50%2F21af670d442692bb03db731afd9b%2F4.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/84422ff/2147483647/strip/true/crop/502x768+0+0/resize/502x768!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F39%2F50%2F21af670d442692bb03db731afd9b%2F4.jpg\" />\n</picture>\n<p>\n</p><figcaption>María Eugenia Hernández, Adriana Anza y Guadalupe Irigoyen.</figcaption><p></p>\n</figure>\n</div><p>Durante el evento, las bodegas ofrecen a los concurrentes grandes descuentos, y también aprovechan la ocasión para presentar muchas de sus novedades, entre ellas, los blancos de la última cosecha.</p><div>\n<figure>\n<picture>\n<img alt=\"Ruben Tribucio y Daniel Menéndez.\" srcset=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/504b9e4/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x728+0+0/resize/1024x728!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F22%2F8a%2F884e8659482aa959519a71b716f5%2F5.jpg 1x, https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/535dc6e/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x728+0+0/resize/2048x1456!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F22%2F8a%2F884e8659482aa959519a71b716f5%2F5.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/504b9e4/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x728+0+0/resize/1024x728!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F22%2F8a%2F884e8659482aa959519a71b716f5%2F5.jpg\" />\n</picture>\n<p>\n</p><figcaption>Ruben Tribucio y Daniel Menéndez.</figcaption><p></p>\n</figure>\n</div><div>\n<figure>\n<picture>\n<img alt=\"Darío Aprea, Carolina Brera y Verónica Álvez.\" srcset=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/a36a068/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x682+0+0/resize/1024x682!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F62%2F0c%2F71888c2541ba99ab091442382317%2F6.jpg 1x, https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/a97dfd7/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x682+0+0/resize/2048x1364!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F62%2F0c%2F71888c2541ba99ab091442382317%2F6.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/a36a068/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1024x682+0+0/resize/1024x682!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F62%2F0c%2F71888c2541ba99ab091442382317%2F6.jpg\" />\n</picture>\n<p>\n</p><figcaption>Darío Aprea, Carolina Brera y Verónica Álvez.</figcaption><p></p>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>¿Encontraste un error?</p>\n<p>\nReportar\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
